msgstr "Group strategy group class"

#: of qteasy.group.Group:1
msgid "策略组，包含多个策略成员，定义了成员策略的信号类型、混合方式、运行频率和时机等属性。"
msgstr ""
"A strategy group containing multiple strategy members, defining properties such as the member "
"strategies' signal type, blending method, run frequency, and timing."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.add_strategy:1
msgid "添加一个策略到组中，策略将成为该组的成员。"
msgstr "Add a strategy to the group; the strategy will become a member of the group."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.add_strategy:3
msgid ""
"新增的策略必须是 BaseStrategy 的实例，并且不能已经是该组的成员，否则将引发 ValueError。 新增策略"
"的 group_id 将被设置为该组的 group_id，以便在策略中访问所属组的信息。"
msgstr ""
"The added strategy must be an instance of BaseStrategy and must not already be a member of this "
"group; otherwise, a ValueError will be raised. The added strategy’s group_id will be set to "
"this group’s group_id so that the strategy can access information about its associated group."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.add_strategy:6
msgid "需要添加到组中的策略实例，必须是 BaseStrategy 的子类实例。"
msgstr ""
"The strategy instance to add to the group; it must be an instance of a subclass of BaseStrategy."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.add_strategy:11
msgid "当 strategy 已经是该组的成员时，抛出 ValueError，提示策略已存在于组中。"
msgstr ""
"If strategy is already a member of the group, raise ValueError indicating that the strategy "
"already exists in the group."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.add_strategy:12 qteasy.group.Group.remove_strategy:12
msgid "当 strategy 不是 BaseStrategy 的实例时，抛出 TypeError，提示策略类型错误。"
msgstr ""
"If strategy is not an instance of BaseStrategy, raise TypeError indicating an invalid strategy "
"type."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.blend:1
msgid "使用当前 blender 将同组策略信号混合为一组信号。"
msgstr ""
"Use the current blender to blend signals from strategies in the same group into a single set of "
"signals."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.clear_strategies:1
msgid "清空组中的所有策略，所有成员策略将不再是该组的成员。"
msgstr ""
"Clear all strategies in the group; all member strategies will no longer be members of this "
"group."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.group_id:1
msgid "Group 的 ID，与 name 相同，用于 Strategy.group_id 兼容"
msgstr "The group's ID, the same as name, for compatibility with Strategy.group_id."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.remove_strategy:1
msgid "从组中移除一个策略，策略将不再是该组的成员。"
msgstr "Remove a strategy from the group; the strategy will no longer be a member of the group."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.remove_strategy:3
msgid ""
"被移除的策略必须是该组的成员，否则将引发 ValueError。 被移除策略的 group_id 将被设置为 None，以"
"表示不再属于任何组。"
msgstr ""
"The removed strategy must be a member of this group; otherwise, a ValueError will be raised. "
"The removed strategy’s group_id will be set to None to indicate that it no longer belongs to "
"any group."

#: of qteasy.group.Group.remove_strategy:6
msgid "需要从组中移除的策略实例，必须是该组的成员。"
